groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: What Would You Do - Take 2
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:short_description: What would you do if you came looking or a cache that later turned out to have been archived?
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description:
Hide another one in (almost) the same spot of course!!!!!
It seems I don't get out to cache as much as I should (must be busy with hiding caches, I guess)and I missed that this one was gone.
No matter, I turned this DNF into another one in my hides column.
Good luck and use the handy pull off to park!
Congrats to The GeoBunch for the FTF honors (their first)!!!!!!!

groundspeak:log.groundspeak:text: Quick find, and I'm glad because it is crazy hot out here. I'm in town for a few days from PA -- 70 degrees there, 100 here.
